items.title: Awesome Cpp
items.content_text:
### Frameworks

*   [JUCE (â­7.4k)](https://github.com/julianstorer/JUCE) - An all-encompassing C++ class library for developing cross-platform software. \[Core-Module: ISC, Rest: GPL2/GPL3/Proprietary] [website](http://www.juce.com/)
*   [Qt](https://github.com/qt) :zap: - A cross-platform application and UI framework. \[GPL/LGPL/Proprietary] [website](https://www.qt.io)

### Audio

*   [KFR](https://www.kfrlib.com/) - Fast, modern C++ DSP framework, FFT, FIR/IIR filters, Sample Rate Conversion. \[GPL/Proprietary]
*   [OpenAL](http://www.openal.org/) - Open Audio Library - A crossplatform audio API. \[BSD/LGPL/Proprietary]

### Documentation

*   [hdoc (â­330)](https://github.com/hdoc/hdoc) - The modern documentation tool for C++. \[AGPL/Proprietary] [website](https://hdoc.io)
*   [Natural Docs (â­213)](https://github.com/NaturalDocs/NaturalDocs) - Natural Docs is an open source documentation generator for multiple programming languages. \[AGPL/Proprietary] [website](https://www.naturaldocs.org)

### GUI

*   [Boden (â­1.7k)](https://github.com/AshampooSystems/boden) - Native, mobile, cross-platform GUI Framework. \[GPL/LGPL/Proprietary] [website](https://www.boden.io)
*   [FLTK](http://www.fltk.org/index.php) - Fast, light, cross-platform C++ GUI toolkit. \[LGPL2]
*   [Slint (â­20k)](https://github.com/slint-ui/slint) - Lightweight GUI toolkit for desktop and embedded. \[GPL/Free/Proprietary] [website](https://slint.dev/)

### Graphics

*   [Harfang 3D (â­620)](https://github.com/harfang3d/harfang3d) 3D visualization library usable in C++, Python, Lua and Go. Based on BGFX. \[GPLv3/LGPLv3/Proprietary] [website](https://www.harfang3d.com)

### Memory Allocation

*   [Hoard (â­1.2k)](https://github.com/emeryberger/Hoard) - Fast, Scalable, and Memory-efficient Malloc for Linux, Windows, and Mac. \[Apache-2.0] [website](http://hoard.org/)

### PDF

*   [MuPDF](https://mupdf.com/) - A lightweight PDF, XPS, and E-book viewer. \[AGPL/Proprietary]

### Regular Expression

*   [SLRE (â­538)](https://github.com/cesanta/slre) - Super Light Regexp engine for C/C++. \[GPLv2/Proprietary]

### Web Application Framework

*   [Wt](http://www.webtoolkit.eu/wt) - A C++ library for developing web applications. \[GPL/Proprietary]

### Miscellaneous

*   [Remote Call Framework](http://www.deltavsoft.com/) - Inter-process communication framework for C++. \[GPL2/Proprietary]
